OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,FAn ITV News investigation has found
OL,7,Fsome pupils across England are being
OL,8,Ftaught in dangerous, filthy conditions
OL,9,Fand by unqualified staff, as Social
OL,10,FAffairs Correspondent Sarah Corker
OL,11,Freports
OL,13,FThere are warnings that thousands of
OL,14,Fchildren are being hidden away in
OL,15,Fsuspected illegal or unregistered
OL,16,Fschools across England, labelled
OL,17,F"breeding grounds for extremism", and
OL,18,Freceiving a substandard education.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
