PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781693268
OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,FAn ITV News investigation has found
OL,7,Fsome pupils are learning in dangerous,
OL,8,Ffilthy conditions, and being taught by
OL,9,Funqualified staff, with many left
OL,10,Funable to properly read or write
OL,11,FEnglish.
OL,13,FIn an exclusive interview, former
OL,14,FChief Inspector of Ofsted Sir Michael
OL,15,FWilshaw said: "If children at these
OL,16,Fschools are getting a narrow
OL,17,Fcurriculum and don't have access to
OL,18,Fthe same opportunities as others, then
OL,19,Fsegregation will increase, divisions
OL,20,Fwill increase and extremism will
OL,21,Fincrease."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781693268
OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,FSir Michael set up Ofsted's illegal
OL,7,Fschools team after witnessing the
OL,8,Fissue first hand in Birmingham in
OL,9,F2016, and remains deeply concerned
OL,10,Fthat thousands of children may still
OL,11,Fbe at significant risk.
OL,13,F"We know people who haven't been
OL,14,Fvetted or had police checks are
OL,15,Fteaching stuff that would not be
OL,16,Fallowed in mainstream schools," he
OL,17,Fadded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
