OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781693268
OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,FBy law, anywhere providing full-time
OL,7,Feducation, defined as 18 hours or more
OL,8,Fa week, to five or more kids must
OL,9,Fregister as a school and be inspected
OL,10,F- but many don't and go under the
OL,11,Fradar.
OL,13,FOthers use loopholes in the legal
OL,14,Fdefinition of a school, claiming that
OL,15,Fthey operate only for a limited number
OL,16,Fof hours to evade oversight.
OL,18,FITV News has identified more than 20
OL,19,Fsuspected illegal schools in London,
OL,20,FLeicester and Manchester.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
