PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781693268
OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,FWe have spoken to five former students
OL,7,Fand whistleblowers from across the
OL,8,Fcountry who were all critical of the
OL,9,Fsegregated education they received.
OL,11,F'It's very painful to speak about'
OL,13,FMoshi's sons attend unregistered
OL,14,F'yeshivas' in an ultra-orthodox Jewish
OL,15,Fcommunity in London.
OL,17,FThe main focus is on religious
OL,18,Fteaching, with boys spending up to 15
OL,19,Fhours a day in these settings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781693268
OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,FMoshi, not his real name, is afraid to
OL,7,Fspeak out because of the strict rules
OL,8,Fof his community, so we've protected
OL,9,Fhis identity.
OL,11,FHe warns that the majority of boys who
OL,12,Fattend unregistered yeshivas are left
OL,13,Filliterate and innumerate at the age
OL,14,Fof 16.
OL,16,F"They don't learn any skills,
OL,17,Fnothing," he told ITV News. "No
OL,18,Fcomputers, no science, not even basic
OL,19,Fmaths.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781693268
OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,F"These boys don't know their
OL,7,Ftimetables when they leave school at
OL,8,F16. They can do ABCs like little
OL,9,Fchildren, they don't know what a
OL,10,Fparagraph means. It's very painful to
OL,11,Fspeak about it."
OL,13,FThose who run these unregistered
OL,14,Fyeshivas argue they are places of
OL,15,Freligious study, not schools, and
OL,16,Ftherefore don't have to abide by the
OL,17,Fsame rules. Yet it is the only
OL,18,Feducation Moshi's sons get.
OL,26,@sD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781693268
OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,F"The yeshiva system isn't being
OL,7,Fregulated in any way, shape or form,"
OL,8,Fhe said. "It's completely under the
OL,9,Fradar, nobody is checking or vetting
OL,10,Fthe teachers, there's no training."
OL,12,FMoshi said that he can't move his sons
OL,13,Fto another school, or criticise them
OL,14,Fpublicly, because he'd be ostracised
OL,15,Ffrom his community, and he wants to
OL,16,Fchange things from within.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
