OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781693268
OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,F"To speak out to someone outside of
OL,7,Fthe community, it's considered one of
OL,8,Fthe biggest crimes you can do," he
OL,9,Fsaid. "Culture is important, identity
OL,10,Fis important, but there has to be a
OL,11,Fbalance."
OL,13,FThree former students have told us
OL,14,Fthey learned in squalid conditions in
OL,15,Fsimilar unregistered yeshivas, and
OL,16,Fthey've struggled to find work or
OL,17,Fcommunicate in English.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/29
