PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781693268
OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,FThere have been 1,839 Ofsted
OL,7,Finvestigations into suspected illegal
OL,8,Fschools over the last decade. The
OL,9,Fhighest number is in London, with 335
OL,10,Finvestigations, and in Yorkshire,
OL,11,Fwhere there have been 266.
OL,13,FOf those inspected, almost a fifth
OL,14,Fwere religious schools and
OL,15,Fpredominantly Christian, Jewish and
OL,16,FMuslim.
OL,18,FThose found running an illegal school
OL,19,Fcan face up to six months in prison,
OL,20,Fan unlimited fine, or both.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781693268
OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,FYet Ofsted's illegal schools team has
OL,7,Fhistorically secured few successful
OL,8,Fprosecutions - only nine prosecutions
OL,9,Fto date - due to legislative loopholes
OL,10,Fand evidence gathering restrictions.
OL,12,FThe first ever prosecution was in
OL,13,FLondon in 2018, when inspectors found
OL,14,Fthe Al-Istiqamah Learning Centre,
OL,15,FSouthall, with 58 children, being
OL,16,Fdenied a proper education.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781693268
OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,FThe headteacher and director were each
OL,7,Fgiven a three-month nighttime curfew
OL,8,Fand also ordered to pay #400 each in
OL,9,Fcosts. Both were later banned from
OL,10,Fmanaging or teaching in any school in
OL,11,FEngland.
OL,13,FIn 2019 and 2021, inspectors found
OL,14,FAmbassadors High School, in Streatham,
OL,15,FSouth London, was "wilfully neglecting
OL,16,Fsafeguarding".
OL,18,FEvidence of learning materials
OL,19,Fdiscovered at the site encouraged
OL,20,Fparents to hit their children if they
OL,21,Fdid not pray.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781693268
OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,FThis case resulted in the first-ever
OL,7,Fprison sentence for this offence. The
OL,8,Fheadteacher received an eight-week
OL,9,Fprison sentence, suspended for 12
OL,10,Fmonths, after she continued to run the
OL,11,Fschool following a previous conviction.
OL,13,FIn the Midlands in 2019, Freiston Hall
OL,14,Ffor vulnerable children charged six
OL,15,Fcouncils tens of thousands of pounds
OL,16,Fdespite being unregistered, unsafe,
OL,17,Fand with unvetted staff.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781693268
OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,FMore recently, the operators of The
OL,7,FLambs Christian School in Birmingham
OL,8,Fwere prosecuted following serious
OL,9,Fsafeguarding concerns in 2024.
OL,11,F'Dickensian conditions, no access to
OL,12,Fdaylight, no drinking water'
OL,14,FFor 10 years, Victor Shafiee headed up
OL,15,FOfsted's illegal schools team. The
OL,16,Fhorrific conditions he witnessed have
OL,17,Fnever left him.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31916
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781693268
OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,F"I found a room next to open sewers,
OL,7,Frat droppings, holes on the wall. In
OL,8,Fdisused industrial estates, Dickensian
OL,9,Fconditions, no access to daylight, no
OL,10,Fdrinking water."
OL,12,FMr Shafiee retired earlier this year,
OL,13,Fbut in a rare interview told ITV News
OL,14,Fthat the authorities were struggling
OL,15,Fto tackle the scale of the problem.
OL,17,F"All my senses tell me what we've seen
OL,18,Fso far is the tip of the iceberg," Mr
OL,19,FShafiee said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@PO]yD@AOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31917
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781693268
OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,FVictor Shafiee, who headed up Ofsted's
OL,7,Fillegal schools team for a decade,
OL,8,Ftold ITV News he fears 'children are
OL,9,Fbeing radicalised' in unregulated
OL,10,Fsettings
OL,12,FHe warned the issue had been
OL,13,F"deprioritised" under the current
OL,14,FChief Inspector of Ofsted Sir Martyn
OL,15,FOliver and added that Ofsted didn't
OL,16,Fhave the resources needed.
OL,18,F"Year on year the budget for this work
OL,19,Funder the new chief inspector has been
OL,20,Fcut," he said.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31918
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781693268
OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,F"I'm really worried about it. I fear
OL,7,Fchildren being radicalised, I fear
OL,8,Fchildren's lives being destroyed."
OL,10,FBecause of the shadowy nature of these
OL,11,Finstitutions, estimates vary from
OL,12,F6,000 children in illegal schools
OL,13,Facross England to tens of thousands,
OL,14,Faccording to one former Ofsted boss.
OL,16,FMany sites do not do criminal records
OL,17,Fchecks on staff, some of whom have no
OL,18,Fbackground in teaching, according to
OL,19,FOfsted.
OL,26,@pD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31919
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781693268
OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,F'There was a lot of instillment of
OL,7,Ffear of the outside world'
OL,9,FConnections have also been made
OL,10,Fbetween home schooling and illegal
OL,11,Fsettings, as Sir Wilshaw warned "we
OL,12,Fshould be really worried about home
OL,13,Feducation being used as a cover for
OL,14,Fthese sorts of institutions".
OL,16,FThe majority of those attending these
OL,17,Fillegal settings are technically home-
OL,18,Fschooled children, but the reality is
OL,19,Fthat some are cut off from mainstream
OL,20,Fsociety with little or no safeguarding
OL,21,Fchecks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
