OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31920
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781693268
OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,FFrom the age of six, Alice Benskin was
OL,7,Fhome-schooled in a rural part of the
OL,8,FMidlands and taught using a
OL,9,Ffundamentalist Christian learning
OL,10,Fprogramme, which she claims still
OL,11,Fpromotes misogyny today.
OL,13,F"It's like a cult," she told ITV News.
OL,14,F"That's the only way I can describe
OL,15,Fit, you're very controlled."
OL,17,FMs Benskin claims she was groomed to
OL,18,Fbe a "godly wife" from a very young
OL,19,Fage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/29
