OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,F"We weren't really encouraged as women
OL,7,Fto have equal rights," she said. "It
OL,8,Fwas very much that the man is the head
OL,9,Fof the home and that women, girls,
OL,10,Fwere subservient to men.
OL,12,F"I was very scared," she added. "I
OL,13,Fthink there was a lot of instillment
OL,14,Fof fear of the outside world."
OL,16,FAlice Benskin was taught using a
OL,17,Ffundamentalist Christian learning
OL,18,Fprogramme from the age of six and
OL,19,Fdescribed it as 'damaging'
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
