FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31922
SC,0022
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781693268
OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,FWhile not illegal, the learning
OL,7,Fprogramme is controversial, and some
OL,8,Fparts of it are still used today
OL,9,Facross the country. Comic-like
OL,10,Ftextbooks were Ms Benskin's main
OL,11,Fsource of learning as a child.
OL,13,FHer learning was almost entirely bible-
OL,14,Fbased, and the qualifications she did
OL,15,Fobtain held no weight in the outside
OL,16,Fworld.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G22/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31923
SC,0023
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781693268
OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,FThe textbooks taught students that the
OL,7,F"probability of evolution is next to
OL,8,Fimpossible", while lessons on gender
OL,9,Fdescribed women's roles as "helper,
OL,10,Fcook, cleans house, washes and irons
OL,11,Fclothes", and that young girls should
OL,12,F"obey and help".
OL,14,FOne science textbook page seemingly
OL,15,Fconfirms the existence of the Loch
OL,16,FNess Monster, and another teaches that
OL,17,Fthe "probability of evolution is next
OL,18,Fto impossible".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G23/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31924
SC,0024
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781693268
OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,FITV News has seen textbooks stating
OL,7,Fthat homosexuality was a "learned
OL,8,Fbehaviour" and that "extensive
OL,9,Fbiological tests prove this".
OL,11,FMs Benskin said: "It is really
OL,12,Fdamaging, really, really damaging, to
OL,13,Fbe indoctrinated with these beliefs to
OL,14,Flive under this level of control and
OL,15,Fisolation."
OL,17,FOfsted is expected to get greater
OL,18,Fpowers to inspect and prosecute these
OL,19,Funregistered settings in September
OL,20,F2027.
OL,26,@sD@ROU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G24/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
