OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31925
SC,0025
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781693268
OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,FCurrently, inspectors have limited
OL,7,Fpowers to search or seize evidence, or
OL,8,Fenter a setting suspected of being an
OL,9,Fillegal school. Under the new
OL,10,Flegislation, this will change.
OL,12,FThe Children's Wellbeing and Schools
OL,13,FBill will also create a home school
OL,14,Fregister providing greater oversight
OL,15,Fof those not in mainstream education.
OL,17,FYet experts warn that these new legal
OL,18,Fduties and powers will be "useless" if
OL,19,Fthere is no extra funding or resources
OL,20,Ffrom central government to use them
OL,21,Feffectively.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G25/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31926
SC,0026
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781693268
OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,FOfsted's current Chief Inspector, Sir
OL,7,FMartyn Oliver told ITV News: "We have
OL,8,Frepeatedly raised concerns that
OL,9,Fthousands of children may be attending
OL,10,Fsuch settings, where they are
OL,11,Fpotentially at risk of serious harm.
OL,13,F"But a historical lack of legal power
OL,14,Fhas hampered our efforts to deal with
OL,15,Fthese places, many of which have
OL,16,Fexploited loopholes in the law to
OL,17,Fcontinue operating under the radar,
OL,18,Favoiding regulation and scrutiny.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G26/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31927
SC,0027
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781693268
OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,F"We have successfully lobbied for new
OL,7,Fpowers to strengthen our ability to
OL,8,Finvestigate and take meaningful action
OL,9,Fagainst illegal schools, which we will
OL,10,Fsoon have under the Children's
OL,11,FWellbeing and Schools Act.
OL,13,F"We are determined to use these new
OL,14,Fpowers to drive the scourge of illegal
OL,15,Fschools out of our country."
OL,17,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,18,FEducation said the government "will
OL,19,Fnot tolerate settings that operate
OL,20,Foutside the law or put children's
OL,21,Ffutures at risk".
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G27/29
