OL,3,CThousands of children at risk in
OL,4,C'dirty and dangerous' illegal schools
OL,6,F"That's why through the Children's
OL,7,FWellbeing and Schools Act we are
OL,8,Fstrengthening Ofsted's powers to
OL,9,Finvestigate suspected unregistered
OL,10,Fschools and giving councils new tools
OL,11,Fto identify children who are not
OL,12,Freceiving a suitable education," they
OL,13,Fadded.
OL,15,FFor help and support visit:
OL,17,FIf you or anyone you know has a story
OL,18,Fto share, you can get in touch by
OL,19,Femailing: socialaffairs@itv.com
